Data Analysis with R

Materials for the first session of the spring 2025 workshop series, “Data Analysis with R”, for Bucknell Faculty and Staff.

This day covers:

  • Workshop goals
  • An introduction to R and RStudio
  • An introduction to and engagement with Quarto documents.
